1276d4bc4f6fc653d424ccef5c7af36d453ba11f","tid":1242241,"uid":57378,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"Unsw 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb41c5c29b152301a79c9fdcde60b16f3c173cb","tid":1242241,"uid":257422,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c1781fc675f3d77a9efe18e257a107382c5a48","tid":1242241,"uid":57378,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:02:31.000Z","msg":"其實大家點睇佢入邊嗰個faculty student ratio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佔成20%大家覺得會唔會太多？"},{"pid":"0b8a9f9375aa8ddd0ec449fc9d258432cf039657","tid":1242241,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"仲睇QS打飛機"},{"pid":"520f614d6e7749d36e559dbb7b7856b4fb4942a1","tid":1242241,"uid":28641,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"現實<br />\nHKU grad<br />\n月入兩皮住公屋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: HKU grad 三層私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7343ca89d5cb12be2da0856eee824d873e4409b8","tid":1242241,"uid":516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"我城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bcead295b5e2c79355bf95e75dae3772142e6a","tid":1242241,"uid":92064,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"教大呢，人工屌打8大喎"},{"pid":"f68d198c19bfc9fb0c095eec2e90e2a0bf516b8f","tid":1242241,"uid":120918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5965203ccd8e1d9b4106ca53f6770de6483bc05d","tid":1242241,"uid":179714,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:54:12.000Z","msg":"HSU呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cl